(Your result here)

TC-ST03 – Validate Navigation Buttons (View Project / More Info)

Objective: Confirm that buttons inside Softr collections open the correct pages.

Steps:

1 - Open the Softr homepage.

2 - Scroll to the “Projects” or “Portfolio” collection.

3 - Hover over a project card.

4 - Identify the button “View Project” or similar.

5 - Click the button.

6 - Observe the redirect.

7 - Verify that the new page shows the correct project details.

8 - Navigate back using browser back arrow.

Expected Result:
Button correctly opens the matching project; content belongs to that item.

